{"tid":1147382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【海關油麻地冚老翻　檢獲逾千隻盜版及色情光碟】","createTime":"2019-05-09T22:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T03:47:17.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"583faab4c90e55ef0dab3f11ccfbbdde3fd2607f","tid":1147382,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T22:38:05.000Z","msg":"香港海關昨日（5月8日）在油麻地採取反盜版行動，檢獲約5600隻懷疑盜版光碟和約3000隻懷疑色情光碟，估計市值約23萬元。<br />\n<br />\n行動中，海關人員搜查兩間位於油麻地的店舖，檢獲約5600隻懷疑盜版光碟，主要為市面上流行的電影及電視劇，以及約3000隻懷疑色情光碟，並拘捕兩名分別為49歲及71歲男子。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/05-09-2019/52861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F05-09-2019%2F52861&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGmg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=8c5683d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/05-09-2019/52861</a><br />\n<br />\n#色情光碟 #盜版<br />\n<br />\n請支持PassionPrime：<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/prime/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Fprime%2F&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGmg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=d0e56a05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/prime/</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血時報印刷版︰<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2F4.0%2Fregform.php&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGmg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=f22edb0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血文青課金計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise2&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGmg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=4b1d264b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise2</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血主持育成計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGmg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=3725b5b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise</a><br />\n<br />\n《熱血時報》 iOS，Android 同步抗共，歡迎下載：<br />\n<br />\niPhone<br />\n<a href=\"https://apple.co/2IfgPoP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple.co%2F2IfgPoP&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGmg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=0e900c17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apple.co/2IfgPoP</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2HqB4Q4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HqB4Q4&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGmg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=421ab441\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2HqB4Q4</a><br />\n--------------------<br />\n成功之前，我們絕對不要放棄夢想！<br />\nTill our dreams come true, we'll fight on."},{"pid":"0567ab43324f7e1fff685d90741a996a09eff342","tid":1147382,"uid":245180,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T22:40:25.000Z","msg":"71歲呀伯都趕？搵食姐........."},{"pid":"b01dbfdf3a704917fae603d97ee5902d8e6affa4","tid":1147382,"uid":40470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T22:48:04.000Z","msg":"夕陽工業"},{"pid":"cf20e893cf0c71eb352403acfc3bd7fd76775599","tid":1147382,"uid":144464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:19:03.000Z","msg":"重有人買咸碟？？"},{"pid":"ce21d2fc58c6f7d72b09c09e8900a14afa8898f0","tid":1147382,"uid":70183,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:31:20.000Z","msg":"呢啲非物質文化遺產黎喎"},{"pid":"e4e0b1c2e8bec9807a777f0fc0889aa2ba0a5d6d","tid":1147382,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:34:23.000Z","msg":"咸碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢盤生意隨時無肉食"},{"pid":"3b7fb7106b63cd4592837a162f18e60948226